li.p:
We evaluate the function for t=\alert{7}. To follow the order of operations, we simplify the power before multiplying by 10. ~\alert{\text{[TK]}}
        P(\alert{7}) = 10 \cdot 2^{\alert{7}/5} \approx 10(2.639)=26.39
        After one week there will be 26 fleas.

